review_blob: From the start the beer has a beautiful dark color with a velvety head to the pour. The chocolate and coffee malts make for a rich creamy taste with just a slight bite to the finish. This beer is so smooth and easy to drink and as much as I wish that the glass would never end the 9% abv sadly leaves me to only a glass at a time.
beer_name: Tractor Brewing Luna de los Muertos
